   Feature: Etsy
  
  @StepDef
  Scenario: I am a first time user on Esty
      Given I navigate to "https://www.etsy.com/au/"
        And the heading can be located by id "etsy-logo"
        And the cart icon title can be located by class name "cart "
        And the heading should be "Etsy"
        And the cart icon title should be "Cart"

  @StepDef
  Scenario: the about information is selected
     Given the About link can be located by javascript "$('#footer-about-link-desktop').get(0)"
       And I scroll to the top of the About link
       And I click the About link
  
  @StepDef 
  Scenario: I go to find out more about Esty
      Given the about information is selected
        And I wait until "$('.about-banner').text().trim() == 'About Etsy'"
       Then I am on the About page

  @StepDef
  Scenario: I should be presented with About information
      Given I am on the About page
